README

Spoke calculator for bicycle wheels written in python 2.7

!! Version 0.0.1 only supports front wheels without disc brakes (symmetric wheels) !!

All measures necessary to calculate the spoke length are
given to spoke_calculator.py as command-line options.

To see which options are required see:

./spoke_calculator.py --help




Changelog:

v0.0.1:
- first commit


